---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { timelineItems } from '../lib/utils';
---

<BaseLayout title="Sobre">
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <section class="sobre-hero relative py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-40 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-rose/10 via-brand-bg to-brand-champagne/10"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-brand-rose/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

    <div class="container-premium relative z-10 text-center">
      <span class="badge mb-6 inline-flex animate-slide-up">Sobre Nós</span>
      <h1 class="heading-xl text-brand-graphite mb-6 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        A História da <span class="text-gradient">Brubru Nails</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-body text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        Mais de duas décadas de paixão, dedicação e amor pelas unhas — transformados em ferramentas que ajudam Nail Designers a conquistar o sucesso que merecem.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Timeline Section */}
  <section id="jornada" class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-premium">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20">
        <span class="badge mb-4 inline-block">Jornada</span>
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-brand-graphite mb-4">Minha Jornada</h2>
        <p class="text-body text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          De apaixonada por unhas a referência nacional
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 md:-translate-x-px top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-rose/20 via-brand-champagne/40 to-brand-rose/20"></div>

        <div class="space-y-12 md:space-y-16">
          {timelineItems.map((item, index) => {
            const isEven = index % 2 === 0;
            return (
              <div
                class:list={[
                  'timeline-item relative flex items-start gap-6 md:gap-0',
                  isEven ? 'md:flex-row' : 'md:flex-row-reverse',
                ]}
              >
                <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-brand-rose border-4 border-white shadow-medium z-10 mt-1.5"></div>

                <div class:list={[
                  'ml-12 md:ml-0 md:w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)]',
                  isEven ? 'md:pr-8 md:text-right' : 'md:pl-8 md:text-left',
                ]}>
                  <div class="card-premium">
                    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 mb-3 text-xs font-heading font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase bg-brand-champagne/10 text-brand-champagne rounded-full">
                      {item.year}
                    </span>
                    <h3 class="heading-sm text-brand-graphite mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
                    <p class="text-body text-muted">{item.description}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hidden md:block md:w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)]"></div>
              </div>
            );
          })}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Mission & Values Section */}
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-bg">
    <div class="container-premium">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20">
        <span class="badge mb-4 inline-block">Missão e Valores</span>
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-brand-graphite mb-4">O que nos move</h2>
        <p class="text-body text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Acreditamos que toda Nail Designer merece acesso a ferramentas que transformem seu talento em um negócio de sucesso.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="card-premium text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-brand-rose/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-rose" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-brand-graphite mb-3">Paixão</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-muted">Cada produto nasce do amor genuíno pelo mercado das unhas e pela transformação que ele proporciona na vida das profissionais.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-premium text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-brand-champagne/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-champagne" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-brand-graphite mb-3">Inovação</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-muted">Combinamos décadas de experiência com ferramentas modernas para oferecer soluções que realmente funcionam no dia a dia.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-premium text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-brand-rose/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-rose" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-brand-graphite mb-3">Empoderamento</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-muted">Nossa missão é ver cada Nail Designer alcançar um patamar que ela nem imaginava possível — e nos orgulhamos de fazer isso acontecer.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-premium text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-brand-champagne/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-champagne" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-brand-graphite mb-3">Confiança</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-muted">Mais de 20 anos construindo credibilidade. Cada conteúdo que criamos é respaldado por experiência real no mercado.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-premium text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-brand-rose/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-rose" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-brand-graphite mb-3">Resultados</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-muted">Não vendemos promessas — entregamos ferramentas comprovadas que geram resultados reais para quem se compromete.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-premium text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-brand-champagne/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-champagne" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="heading-sm text-brand-graphite mb-3">Ensino</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-muted">Acreditamos que compartilhar conhecimento é a forma mais poderosa de multiplicar o sucesso de toda a comunidade.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Stats Section */}
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-graphite to-brand-graphite/95"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, white 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

    <div class="container-premium relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-white mb-4">Números que contam história</h2>
        <p class="text-body text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Cada número representa vidas transformadas, sonhos realizados e profissionais que ousaram crescer.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="heading-xl text-brand-champagne font-bold mb-3">20+</p>
          <p class="text-body text-white/70">anos de experiência</p>
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-brand-champagne/40 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="heading-xl text-brand-champagne font-bold mb-3">Centenas</p>
          <p class="text-body text-white/70">de clientes atendidas</p>
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-brand-champagne/40 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="heading-xl text-brand-champagne font-bold mb-3">Referência</p>
          <p class="text-body text-white/70">nacional no mercado</p>
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-brand-champagne/40 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* CTA Section */}
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-premium text-center">
      <span class="badge mb-6 inline-flex">Próximo Passo</span>
      <h2 class="heading-lg text-brand-graphite mb-6">
        Pronta para transformar seu <span class="text-gradient">negócio</span>?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Agora que conhece nossa história, descubra as ferramentas que criamos para ajudar Nail Designers como você a conquistarem agenda lotada e resultados extraordinários.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/produtos" class="btn-primary">
          Conhecer Produtos
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/contato" class="btn-secondary">
          Fale Conosco
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sobre-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--white) 100%);
  }
</style>
